  "description": "The sub-bass that moves air. filterCutoff=80 sits at the edge of human hearing — felt in the sternum, not heard in the ears. subOctMix=0.7 adds a full octave below. At concert volume this displaces the air in the room. On headphones it is a rumour of a frequency.",
