    "scripture": [
      "80 Hz is heard. The sub octave is felt.",
      "A proper sound system is required to know this note exists.",
      "Headphone listeners will hear a suggestion. Speaker listeners will feel the walls."
    ],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "This is a physical preset. Requires a subwoofer or large speaker system to experience fully. On headphones the sub octave is reduced. ABYSS macro sweeps the darkness filter fully closed — use this to take the preset from infrasonic rumble to silence.",
    "diagnosis": "filterCutoff=80: deep hadal column — maximum darkness within practical range. subOctMix=0.7: the sub octave is the feature. pressureAmt=0.7: significant compression, the ocean is present. filterRes=0.25: low resonance to prevent peaks at inaudible frequencies. This is the deepest playable pitch in the collection."
